reviews.review_text: stellar Another great download courtesy of charlie miller. It's amazing to hear a concert recorded 37 years ago sound this good. Do yourself a favor and search the charlie miller shows in the archive search engine. You'll get a list of top notch shows with killer sound to boot!

Cosmic Wheels Keep On Turning It's nice to know in this day and age that the cosmic wheels are still in tune when a wonderful source like this spins out for us to enjoy! If there is a better sounding soundboard on the IA I can't remember what it is. It's nice knowing that these reels fell into good hands. Thank you so much!
As for the show itself, well it happens to be one of the strongest shows the band played that year, or any year for that matter. The Dead are definitely ON! The energy level is very high. The whole show is tight and the playing is stellar. The whole band is incredible sync, no blown verses, nobody missing any changes and in tune. A classic! As good as it gets.

PRIMAL DEAD This whole show is a quintessential addition to any head's or casual listener's collection. 

Charlie's transfer brings new life to this sbd. I saw the popular audience tape of this show popping up all over the place. 

Despite the popularity of the aud recording, its REALLY nice to have a great mix.

Absolute 5/5 

5 for concert performance
5 for transfer

this is the classic g-dead lineup at its best.
Glorious show Wow, the energy, and the playing. It doesn't get much better than this, plus right in the heart of my favorite period.
